sys_hub_action_type_definition.annotation: Updates Item Properties of an Artifact
sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Attach and modify properties to an item (file or folder). When a folder is used property attachment is recursive by default.
Leave a value empty to remove a key.
sys_hub_action_type_definition.name: JFrog Artifactory Update Item Properties
